{"type": "article", "id": 7743, "title": "Jack Daniel’s 香氛蜡烛", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-25T07:37:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234601rQDNiOnlBLkWVHgY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t最近，创意公司 Cool Material 利用回收的 Jack Daniel’s 酒瓶制作了一款 Maple Bourbon 香氛蜡烛。瓶身由 Jack Daniel’s 的经典酒瓶打磨而成，蜡烛则采用了 100% 的清洁燃烧大豆制成，加上威士忌本身的酒香，营造出浪漫的香氛环境，每一瓶可以燃烧使用 70 个小时。目前产品定价为 29.95 美元，<a href=\"http://shop.coolmaterial.com/products/maple-bourbon-soy-wax-candle-in-jack-whiskey-bourbon-bottle/?utm_source=CMBlog&amp;utm_medium=CMBlogPost&amp;utm_campaign=JackCandle/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234559X4eGrgFC3RZ6nA9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.99152542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234559jO5pxXtcH3TwLNEP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.99360341\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}